item.title: (poll) what kind of music do you guys listen to?
item.dc:creator: Pinewoodog
item.description:
nep:

they don’t sound like the future bass I hear from Auxy.

It’s because in Auxy, producers are somewhat limited by the effects and sounds (ex. silk is the only supersaw, and fb is all about supersaws), so they make do with what they have and the genre it ends up being closest to is Future Bass. Then, once the “popular” Auxy producers call it Future Bass (as FB is already popular), everybody does.

Also, Auxy is great for wub-wubs, so it’s a genre people are attracted to (I guess?)

Trap Beat + Supersaw + Wubs + 808 Trap Bass = Future Bass
